<i>Trying to snatch the wind</i>

43:04.160 --> 43:07.800
<i>Who really knows?</i>

43:10.520 --> 43:13.640
<i>The clock on your wall</i>

43:14.160 --> 43:17.400
<i>It is filled with sand</i>

43:17.800 --> 43:21.000
<i>Put your hand in mine</i>

43:21.640 --> 43:25.080
<i>And let us be forever</i>

43:25.160 --> 43:28.400
<i>Now you make your choice</i>

43:28.480 --> 43:33.440
<i>And throw us</i>
