43:33.520 --> 43:37.120
<i>But I can forgive you</i>

43:39.720 --> 43:42.920
<i>You are very close to death</i>

43:43.520 --> 43:46.240
<i>But your eye still clear</i>

43:46.320 --> 43:49.800
<i>Does it recognize me? I'm ready</i>

43:49.880 --> 43:54.520
<i>To seek immortality with you</i>
